# BeatportDL-UI Project

Go 1.22 monolith with embedded vanilla `web/` (HTML/CSS/JS via `go:embed`). No frontend build step.

## Paths

- Config: `~/.config/beatportdl-ui/config.yml`
- OAuth credentials: `~/.config/beatportdl-ui/beatportdl-credentials.json`
- Default port: **8989** (falls back to 8990 if busy)
- Beatport API: `https://api.beatport.com/v4`

## Verify changes

```bash
go build ./...
```

No `*_test.go` files yet. Do not commit unless the user asks.

## Feature skills

Repeatable workflows live in `.claude/skills/`. For catalog search, read `.claude/skills/beatport-catalog-search/SKILL.md` before changing search backend or UI.

## UI navigation

Top bar (not sidebar): Search | Download | Queue | Fix Tags | Settings. Search is the default view.
